Re: Newbie the alphabet
by astaroth » Tue 12.01.2009 12:16 pm "Rome wasn't built in a day" (...「ちりも積もれば山となる」でしょうか)It takes years to master any language, a bit more for something as alien as Japanese. Though the grammar is pretty straightforward and no declinations, almost no irregular verbs. Take one step at a time ...
